哈喽大家好我是王刚
Hello everyone, this is Wang Gang

本期视频为大家带来一道特色菜
In this video, I'll introduce a specialty dish

馒头炸虾球
Fried Prawn Balls with Steamed Buns

首先我们把大虾去头
First, remove the head of the prawn

从背部切开
and cut in the back

去除虾线和虾壳
Peel and devein the prawns

然后加入食用盐和柠檬汁
Then marinate the prawns with salt and lemon juice

将虾肉腌制十分钟
for 10 minutes

下一步我们准备一个白馒头
Next, prepare a white steamed bun

将馒头切成大小均匀的小粒备用
Cut the bun into even sized small dices

然后将腌制好的大虾先沾上淀粉再裹上蛋液
Coat the prawns first with starch, and then with egg wash

最后再均匀裹上馒头粒
and finally with the bun dices

再用手轻轻压紧
Press it lightly to make it firmer

锅中油温六成热下入馒头虾
Heat oil to 60%, and then add in the prawns

开中小火炸五分钟
Fry them over low to medium heat for 5 minutes

将虾炸至金黄酥脆的时候倒出备用
until golden brown. Then take out the prawns

然后锅中加入适量的蕃茄酱
and add in a moderate amount of ketchup

翻炒均匀之后加入白糖两勺
Stir fry it, and then add in two spoons of white sugar

再加入少许白醋
and a little white vinegar

然后加入适量的水淀粉收紧汤汁
Then add some starch slurry to thicken the sauce

最后加入炸好的虾球下锅翻炒均匀即可
Finally, add in the fried prawn balls and mix them up with the sauce

一道非常美味的馒头炸虾球就制作完成
Now, a very delicious dish of fried prawn balls with steamed buns is done!

硬核家常菜
馒头炸虾球
大虾：300克
馒头一个、柠檬、鸡蛋
调料：盐、淀粉
蕃茄酱、白糖、白醋
Hardcore home-cooked dish
Fried Prawn Balls with Steamed Buns
Prawns: 300g
One steamed bun, lemon, eggs
Seasonings: salt, starch,
ketchup, white sugar, white vinegar
